name: Shooter (TechHJ)
description:
This is just a basic shooting game which is under development. Be the first to try it. You would face a lot of problems and bugs in the game as it is still under development.  Control keys - 

Click esc button to get back your mouse curzor.

WASD - or arrow keys                                               

R - Reload

Space bar to jump.

If you get stuck at some place use space bar and W to move.

Wish me luck cuz this is my first game.

You can support by donating to harshithj.fam@idfcbank

- Harshith J (Owner)
